description: Our parental relationships are complex and incredibly impactful. Use this workshop to write a letter to your parent(s).

title: Women's Circle: Muses of Our Own Becoming
description: Embrace our dance of contradictions & become your own muse as we weave a new web of integration and interdependence.

title: Grief Navigators
description: This class offers practical tips for processing grief and prompts reflection on our beliefs about grief and loss.

title: Breathing Session for recovery
description: Come practice breathing for hangovers, healing and altitude.

title: Have a Smoother Burn
description: Learn evidence based Acceptance and Mindfulness tools to navigate stormy moments and connect to pleasure on the playa.

title: Ofosho Ramen
description: Come slurp some delish noods with all the toppings with a special RAMEN PARTY on Thurs from 1-3!

title: Sake Roulette Happy Hour
description: Saketinis & Dancing - Invigorate your senses with sake-based cocktails and global sounds before heading out into the evening’s adventures.

title: Type 1 Supply Swap and Meet Up
description: Come by & compare robot parts. Need an extra sensor or have a pod to spare? Need playa tips for cooling insulin? Come!

title: Recognizing Drug Overdoses - NARCAN to Save a Life
description: Come hear how you can recognize drug overdoses and use NARCAN to potentially save a life!

title: Blind Taste Test
description: Vote for the Playa’s best Swiss chocolate spread on bread. Blind taste test.

title: Make Your Own LED Crown/Tiara
description: Stand out in a crowd. Workshop to build your unique LED crown/tiara. Don’t blame us if your friends keep finding you in the night.

title: Spun! Queer Takeover
description:
Spun! an LGBTQI+ dance party and happy hour with music, GoGo dancers and
naked gyro rides for all.

title: Rope Jam
description: Come meet other rope bondage artists to collaborate or learn some basics. Hardpoints for experienced tiers, all levels welcome.

title: Live Visual Sound Journey
description: 8,000 LEDs are synced to three keyboards the artist guides a meditative journey through sound and light. Blending electronic music, hip-hop, jazz, classical, the show is performed live on a mixture of electronic instruments with a heavy emphasis on improvisation — a unique experience never to be played the same again.

title: The Sopurranos: A Sultry Opurratic Duet
description: Watch two critically-acclaimed sopranos, go wild on some of the most moving and entertaining duets in the operatic repertoire, including a frisky feline feature composed by none other than the great Rrrrossini himself! Accompanied by an award-winning pianist and composer this is one purrrrformance you won’t soon forget.

title: Coma and Consciousness
description: Learn about consciousness and disorders of consciousness (coma) and how knowledge of one can inform the other.

title: Science Open Mic
description:
Share YOUR scientific discoveries, musings, and/or journey with sympathetic
academics! Lab coat and whiteboard provided.

title: Lunar Landing
description: Experience ethereal vibes at Lunar Landing: a celestial Node party where Burners unite under the cosmic night.
